    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND CHAPTER 946, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 2011, AS AMENDED BY CHAPTER 922, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 2014, AS AMENDED BY CHAPTER 941, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 2016, AS AMENDED BY CHAPTER 935, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 2018, AS AMENDED BY CHAPTER 909, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 2023, TO EXTEND THE DATE OF REPEAL FROM JULY 1, 2028, TO JULY 1, 2032, ON THE LAW THAT AUTHORIZES THE CITY OF BRANDON, MISSISSIPPI, TO IMPOSE A TAX UPON THE SALE OF PREPARED FOOD AND BEVERAGES IN RESTAURANTS AND BARS WITHIN THE CITY; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
